title: #527 - Jesus Trejo
description:
Jesus Trejo, Comedian seen on Comedy Central and TBS, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt live in studio. Jesus tells Joey and Lee how he has balanced working and growing as a stand up comedian with running his family's landscaping business and taking care of his parents.
